{"word":"H6362 - פָּטַר - pâṭar - paw-tar' - Dismiss","slug":"H6362","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּטַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâṭar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-tar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dismiss"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D8;&#x05E8; - pa&#x0302;t&#x0323;ar</b> - <i>paw-tar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>cleave</i> or burst through, that is, (causatively) to <i>emit</i>, whether literally or figuratively (<i>gape</i>): - dismiss, free, let (shoot) out, slip away."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6358\">H6358</a>, <a href=\"#/H6359\">H6359</a>, <a href=\"#/H6363\">H6363</a>, <a href=\"#/H6364\">H6364</a>, <a href=\"#/H6367\">H6367</a>"}]}